text: Mihály Antos (1879 - April 1937) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1879 births Category:1937 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
